Such is the tragedy that befell Pompeii.

287
00:18:05,610 --> 00:18:08,450
I still have my shift.
Let's part ways here.

288
00:18:09,080 --> 00:18:10,540
The dinner will be ready when you're back.

289
00:18:11,370 --> 00:18:12,380
Thanks!

290
00:18:14,890 --> 00:18:18,620
The seniors are fun to hang around.

291
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:23,220
Fun? More like they are the embodiment
of their respective talent.

292
00:18:24,070 --> 00:18:25,020
Kyouya.

293
00:18:25,820 --> 00:18:26,600
Yes?

294
00:18:28,760 --> 00:18:33,320
You know I draw, don't you?

295
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,440
You have noticed...

296
00:18:39,250 --> 00:18:41,700
It was supposed to be a secret

297
00:18:42,320 --> 00:18:45,930
but I forgot to lock the door back then.

298
00:18:46,260 --> 00:18:48,370
I'm sorry. I shouldn't have looked
without your consent.

299
00:18:48,550 --> 00:18:51,860
It's fine. It's my fault.

300
00:18:54,530 --> 00:18:56,110
Do you still remember what I said?

301
00:18:57,770 --> 00:18:59,880
"Someone who can't do anything

302
00:19:00,070 --> 00:19:03,190
will try his hardest
to find something he can do."

303
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:04,450
Yes.

304
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:08,750
I'm not like everyone. I'm not good at anything.

305
00:19:09,150 --> 00:19:11,950
I make mistakes in my day-to-day life.

306
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:15,340
I'm not good at sports
or studying.

307
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:21,130
The only thing I love...

308
00:19:21,560 --> 00:19:23,450
Is drawing?

309
00:19:24,630 --> 00:19:27,300
But I can't draw well.

310
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:31,200
It has always been just a hobby.

311
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:34,080
I won a prize before

312
00:19:34,440 --> 00:19:37,230
but I can't make a living like that.

313
00:19:37,590 --> 00:19:39,990
And so I thought, if I became a film student,

314
00:19:40,230 --> 00:19:43,120
I could work for the media.

315
00:19:43,710 --> 00:19:45,600
That's why I came to Oonaka.

316
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:49,330
Frankly speaking, I was too afraid
to apply to the Arts Department.

317
00:19:50,250 --> 00:19:53,530
I like drawing, but I don't love it.

318
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:55,040
I am not confident.

319
00:19:55,410 --> 00:19:57,770
That's why I kept it as a secret.

320
00:19:58,630 --> 00:20:00,550
I thought I could be like you.

321
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:05,000
Like one day, I would suddenly have a spotlight.

322
00:20:05,890 --> 00:20:07,580
But that

323
00:20:08,080 --> 00:20:09,440
will never ever happen to me.

324
00:20:09,660 --> 00:20:11,150
Wait, it's because I...

325
00:20:11,290 --> 00:20:12,710
I was thinking.

326
00:20:13,580 --> 00:20:18,550
If I stop drawing, will I find peace?
Will I...

327
00:20:18,860 --> 00:20:19,570
No way!

328
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:24,720
You can't abandon drawing!

329
00:20:25,140 --> 00:20:26,640
Kyouya...?

330
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:29,470
I...

331
00:20:36,590 --> 00:20:38,660
I was touched by your...

332
00:20:41,730 --> 00:20:42,960
I

333
00:20:44,130 --> 00:20:46,590
really like your drawing, Shino Aki.

334
00:20:51,390 --> 00:20:54,240
I've already liked your drawing
from the distant future.

335
00:20:55,760 --> 00:20:59,180
You said that during the shooting.

336
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:03,520
Only I could do it, so you counted on me.

337
00:21:03,980 --> 00:21:05,890
Yes, I did.

338
00:21:06,780 --> 00:21:10,350
I was really happy. Excited too.

339
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:14,300
I keep wondering what's in your mind

340
00:21:15,190 --> 00:21:17,560
and it makes me want to know you better.

341
00:21:21,460 --> 00:21:22,280
I've made up my mind.

342
00:21:22,610 --> 00:21:24,980
I will work hard to be like you.

343
00:21:26,840 --> 00:21:32,090
I will practice more until I can draw
the world you want to see, Kyouya.

344
00:21:32,420 --> 00:21:34,830
Do you have a goal, Kyouya?

345
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:38,710
I do,

346
00:21:38,990 --> 00:21:41,610
but I can't tell you now.

347
00:21:42,430 --> 00:21:44,040
What a shame.

348
00:21:44,480 --> 00:21:48,830
But I'll work hard until you acknowledge me
as your friend.

349
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:51,800
My goal

350
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:56,400
is to make you say the same words
after ten years.

351
00:21:57,550 --> 00:21:59,320
My second life

352
00:21:59,980 --> 00:22:01,490
has just begun.

